          "text": "大将堂堂逞威风，南征北剿立奇功。杨家世代忠心耿，保定宋室锦江洪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫，杨宗保。宋室驾前为臣，官拜统兵大元帅。奉主之命，镇守延安关一带。\n看帅字旗无风自动，定有军情。且等探马一报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双阳讨战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大双阳，竟敢领兵前来讨战。\n左右二先行听令：命你带领三千人马，大战双阳，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "先行甲、先行乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（先行甲、先行乙同上马，四上手引先行甲、先行乙同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双阳武艺高强，他二人只恐不是对手，待老夫城楼观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "营门以外炮声响，\n人有精神马又强。\n刀枪剑戟赛秋霜。\n去到阵前会双阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨宗保上马，四龙套同转场，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去到敌楼看端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨宗保下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
