    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "双阳公主"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（双阳公主急跑上，趟马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玲珑战甲扣连环，胸藏杀人巧机关。恼恨无义狄驸马，因此领兵反延安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家，双阳公主。可恨驸马狄青，在我国招了驸马，暗地盗去我国宝贝。是我\n带兵追赶，也不知他用的怎么法术，将奴吓下马来，他竟自逃走。是奴回至海\n外，不料我二老爹娘，俱被他们杀死。因此招兵聚将，屯军养马，来到延安，\n要与那狠心强盗，见一高下。\n众三军！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙旗、四下手、二女兵同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵伐延安。听吾将令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "西皮倒板",
          "musical_style": "西皮倒板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "来至在战场上传一号令，"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说与大小三军听：\n须要努力往前行。\n回营定斩不容情。\n两军阵前大交兵。\n（四上手、先行甲、先行乙同上，同起打。先行甲、先行乙同败下。四龙旗、四下手、二女兵同跑下。双阳\n公主耍大刀花，下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 6,
          "念": 1,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮",
          "西皮快板"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "杨宗保"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、杨宗保同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨宗保 （四边静） 耳听得战鼓声敲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一阵阵马嘶人闹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也难免血染征袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胜负难保。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨宗保上城。先行甲、先行乙同上，双阳公主追上，打。先行甲、先行乙同下，双阳公主追下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看双阳杀法骁勇，待老夫亲自出马。\n众三军，杀上前去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、杨宗保同出城，同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 3,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "双阳公主",
        "回头便把老将叫",
        "杨宗保"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（双阳公主上，杨宗保上，同起打。杨宗保落马，先行甲上，双阳公主打先行甲下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将被奴托下马，\n霎时叫他染黄沙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虎形上。放火彩。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见猛虎露爪牙。\n走向前来把话答。"
        },
        {
          "character": "回头便把老将叫、杨宗保",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳旁听得有人叹，\n又见双阳在阵前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来的老将通名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅杨宗保。"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是老元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老元帅。可知奴家的来意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主此番前来，无非是为的江山社稷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家此来，一不是为的江山，二不是为的社稷。只求元帅，将吾国驸马狄青，\n唤出城来。吾夫妻见上一面，即刻收兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何难。待老夫调回狄青，与公主见面就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此请老元帅上马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提刀跨金镫，急忙转回营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨宗保下。双阳公主两看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "双阳公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众三军，收兵回营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
