    {
      "scene_index": 9,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘庆",
        "杨宗保",
        "狄青"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、先行甲、先行乙、杨宗保同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼观旌旗起，耳听好消息。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘庆、狄青同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘庆、狄青",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。一旁坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘庆、狄青",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狄青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将小将调回营来，不知有何军情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是你非知：只因你妻双阳，领兵攻打延安，十分骁勇，因此将你调回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狄青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，元帅传令，待小将前去会她一会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狄青听令：命你大战双阳，不得违误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狄青、刘庆",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（狄青、刘庆同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨宗保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带马观阵去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
